profile: I am a small renovation company that specializes in home renovations. I am a licensed red seal carpenter and licensed installer of ICF foundations. I do everything from Foundations to Finish carpentry. This list includes framing, insulating, drywall, drywall finishing, painting, flooring, cabinetry, trim work, window and door installation, siding and roofing. If there is a project you would like help with feel free to give me a call.
